text: Inermoleiopus delkeskampi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1958.Biolib.cz - Inermoleiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1958 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
title: Inermoleiopus delkeskampi
